# 9. Parallel vs Sequential Agents

Multi-agent workflow မှာ agents အားလုံးကို parallel run လုပ်တာ အမြဲမကောင်းပါဘူး။ Task အမျိုးအစားအလိုက် parallel သို့မဟုတ် sequential သွားရမယ်။

## 9.1 Parallel သုံးသင့်တဲ့အချိန်

```text
- Codebase exploration
- PR review by different concerns
- Security / quality / test flakiness review
- Frontend and backend design options research
- Documentation/API behavior verification
```

Example—

```text
Spawn one agent for security review.
Spawn one agent for test coverage review.
Spawn one agent for performance review.
Summarize all findings.
```

## 9.2 Sequential သုံးသင့်တဲ့အချိန်

```text
- SPEC မရှိသေးတဲ့ feature
- Database schema decision
- API contract decision
- Frontend depends on backend contract
- Deployment after tests pass
```

Example—

```text
SPEC Maintainer → Backend Developer → Frontend Developer → Test Engineer → Verifier
```

## 9.3 Rule

```text
Requirement / architecture decision မပြီးခင် implementation agents မလွှတ်ပါနဲ့။
Implementation မပြီးခင် verifier မလွှတ်ပါနဲ့။
Verifier pass မဖြစ်ခင် deployer မလွှတ်ပါနဲ့။
```

